data.description: Reduced for quick sale!!!! Nestled in the quiet, prestigious Bourland Field Estates community, is this stunning recently updated 3-story mansion. No luxurious detail was overlooked as extraordinary features are found throughout the interior, including wood-beamed ceiling & rich hardwood flooring. Spacious primary suite with ensuite bath featuring dual sinks, separate shower, jetted garden tub, and large walk-in closet. 3 levels with an oversized 3 car garage and an attached 2,200 sq. ft. airplane hangar with a Hydro Swing door and it has a helicopter landing pad in the front of the house!!!!! Numerous rooms include: 2 master retreats, 2 large game rooms, 3 large living areas, finished 2800sq ft basement, media room, safe room, and an office. Brand new roof and new HVAC systems.
